♪ ♪

521
00:21:04.132 --> 00:21:05.438
Any leads on a shooter?

522
00:21:07.396 --> 00:21:09.137
A shooter?

523
00:21:09.268 --> 00:21:11.357
No. a car accident.

524
00:21:12.880 --> 00:21:14.098
Locals found her
late last night

525
00:21:14.185 --> 00:21:16.797
