I had no idea.

562
00:23:00.117 --> 00:23:02.119
Never said it out loud before.

563
00:23:02.206 --> 00:23:04.165
[dramatic music plays]

564
00:23:04.295 --> 00:23:05.471
But you...

565
00:23:05.558 --> 00:23:07.342
♪ ♪

566
00:23:07.429 --> 00:23:08.735
[sighs]

567
00:23:08.909 --> 00:23:10.737
