592
00:24:06.009 --> 00:24:07.881
Mecca's not just a connect.

593
00:24:08.011 --> 00:24:09.839
I knew him back in the day.
but I didn't know who he was

594
00:24:09.970 --> 00:24:12.015
'cause I knew him
as somebody else.

595
00:24:12.146 --> 00:24:13.626
Dante Spears. right?

596
