[tense music plays]

597
00:24:15.715 --> 00:24:17.194
Yeah. he paid me a visit.

598
00:24:17.325 --> 00:24:19.588
I know Cane probably told you.

599
00:24:19.719 --> 00:24:20.937
You know. that bag
that we stole from him

600
