Ezekiel Cross.

604
00:24:30.164 --> 00:24:32.906
You knew all that?
Why keep you breathing?

605
00:24:33.036 --> 00:24:35.386
Hid the bag before
he could get to me.

606
00:24:35.474 --> 00:24:37.824
Plus. I'm the only one
that knows where the bag is.

607
00:24:37.954 --> 00:24:40.827
I mean. he made me
hold his tracker shit. but...

608
00:24:40.957 --> 00:24:43.090
