I'm just as good as dead.

609
00:24:43.264 --> 00:24:46.006
♪ ♪

610
00:24:48.487 --> 00:24:49.792
You know them papers also said

611
00:24:49.879 --> 00:24:51.272
that Mecca was a federal
informant too. right?

612
00:24:51.402 --> 00:24:52.839
A fucking snitch?

613
00:24:53.013 --> 00:24:54.405
♪ ♪

614
00:24:54.536 --> 00:24:56.233
Nah. fuck Mecca.
Fuck this nigga.

615
00:24:56.320 --> 00:24:58.975
He deserve every bullet
I'ma put in his ass now.

616
00:24:59.062 --> 00:25:00.847
Mecca think Lorenzo
stole his product.

617
00:25:00.977 --> 00:25:02.675
I'm sure that's what
you told him.

618
00:25:02.805 --> 00:25:04.720
What the fuck else
was I gonna tell this nigga?

619
00:25:04.851 --> 00:25:05.721
He believe me.
but he don't believe

620
00:25:05.852 --> 00:25:07.244
