648
00:26:06.739 --> 00:26:09.655
A quarter shipment will work.
I got a new delivery spot.

649
00:26:09.785 --> 00:26:13.441
Plus. Mecca gets
his payment on time.

650
00:26:17.010 --> 00:26:18.228
So we got a audience

651
