667
00:26:59.182 --> 00:27:02.925
That fucking soldier McVey.
he's Mecca's.

668
00:27:03.056 --> 00:27:04.057
I thought that nigga
was doing me a favor.

669
00:27:04.187 --> 00:27:06.015
He's been keeping tabs on us?

670
00:27:06.146 --> 00:27:08.583
Look. our whole family's
