671
00:27:08.714 --> 00:27:10.585
Do you believe I'll do whatever
it takes to save our children?

672
00:27:10.716 --> 00:27:11.891
Yeah. even when
shit's going bad for us.

673
00:27:12.021 --> 00:27:13.588
