674
00:27:13.719 --> 00:27:15.546
Well. thank you
for giving me that.

675
00:27:15.677 --> 00:27:18.288
Now. Mecca wants you dead.
and he wants Cane to do it.

676
00:27:18.419 --> 00:27:21.117
But we gotta make him believe
that Cane will.

677
00:27:21.204 --> 00:27:23.032
