727
00:29:20.584 --> 00:29:22.586
Fucking Diana.

728
00:29:23.587 --> 00:29:25.459
She was here the other day.
She probably swiped my code.

729
00:29:25.589 --> 00:29:26.677
Diana. what a fucking savage.

730
00:29:28.679 --> 00:29:30.943
Whatever. listen.

731
