Yesterday. man.
you held that shit down. bro.

732
00:29:33.859 --> 00:29:34.773
I really can't even
repay you for that.

733
00:29:36.470 --> 00:29:39.516
But you gotta know that I'm...

734
00:29:39.647 --> 00:29:40.909
I'm outta this shit. B.

735
00:29:41.040 --> 00:29:43.042
-'Riq. come on.
-Bro. I'm out.

736
00:29:43.172 --> 00:29:45.087
A'ight. this is my chance
