737
00:29:45.218 --> 00:29:47.176
just like you
held it down for Trace.

738
00:29:47.307 --> 00:29:49.135
Yes. I know Trace wasn't sick.

739
00:29:49.265 --> 00:29:51.485
I know he was supposed
to testify. but it's all good.

740
00:29:51.572 --> 00:29:54.183
I ain't tripping.
You handled it.

741
00:29:54.314 --> 00:29:55.619
We just can't let
Cane find out.

742
00:29:55.750 --> 00:29:57.317
Facts.

743
00:29:57.447 --> 00:29:59.188
